<% content_for :title, "Help & Support - Concepts" %>

<div class="min-h-screen bg-bg pt-24 pb-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="text-center mb-12">
      <a href="/" class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-text tracking-tight no-underline inline-block mb-4">concepts.</a>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text mb-3">Help & Support</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">We're here to help</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Content -->
    <article class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <!-- FAQ Section -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-text mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">What is concepts.?</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary">concepts. is a microlearning app that delivers powerful mental models in just 2 minutes a day. Each concept includes a clear explanation, a counterintuitive insight, and actionable steps you can apply today.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">How does the subscription work?</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary">Start with a free 3-day trial. After that, it's just $0.99/week. You can cancel anytime through the app. All subscriptions are managed through Apple App Store.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">How do I manage my subscription?</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary">Go to Profile > Manage Subscription > Cancel to cancel your subscription anytime.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">How do I restore my purchases?</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary">Go to Profile > Manage Subscription > Restore to restore your subscription on a new device or after reinstalling the app.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">How many concepts can I generate per day?</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary">All users can generate up to 3 concepts per day. This limit resets daily based on your timezone.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">How do I delete my account?</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary">Go to Settings in the app and tap "Delete Account". Your personal data will be removed, but all generated concepts will stay unlinked from you. This action cannot be undone.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text mb-2">I'm having trouble signing in with Apple</h3>
            <p class="text-text-secondary">Make sure you're using the same Apple ID that you used to sign up. If you're still having issues, try signing out of your Apple ID on your device and signing back in, then try again in the app.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Contact Section -->
      <section class="mb-12 p-6 bg-white border border-border rounded-xl">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-text mb-4">Still need help?</h2>
        <p class="text-text-secondary mb-4">We're here to help! Reach out to us:</p>
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-text-secondary">
            <strong class="text-text">Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:tim@conceptsapp.live" class="text-accent hover:text-accent/80 underline">tim@conceptsapp.live</a>
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-secondary">
            <strong class="text-text">Community:</strong> <a href="https://discord.gg/sAsKjB4a" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent/80 underline">Join our Discord</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Legal Links -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-text mb-4">Legal & Policies</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li>
            <a href="/privacy" class="text-accent hover:text-accent/80 underline">Privacy Policy</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/terms" class="text-accent hover:text-accent/80 underline">Terms of Service</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <footer class="pt-8 mt-12 border-t border-border text-center">
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">concepts. - Upgrade your brain</p>
      </footer>
    </article>
  </div>
</div>
